race.comment: SWING BY (6) clocked a speedy 18.86 finishing second in a Grade 5 at this track last start. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. LUCORA (4) goes very well this course and distance starting six times for two wins and two minors. In the money last time at this track (18.87) in a Grade 5, finishing a 3.5 lengths third. Among the main chances. NOAKI WARRIOR (8) was out of the placings last time but recorded an impressive Grade 6 win (16.68) at this track three runs back. Can feature with the right run. WERINA SPIRIT (3) has ability and finds the right scenario to bounce back.
